Battery Backup Systems
If you are not ready for a full solar installation yet, a battery backup system is a great starting point. We install the batteries and inverter so that when the power goes out, your essential appliances keep running. You can always add solar panels later to charge the batteries from the sun instead of the grid.

Commercial Solar Installations
We install commercial solar systems up to 100kW for businesses, estates, farms, office parks and other large properties. A commercial system can dramatically cut your electricity costs, protect you from load shedding, and reduce your reliance on the grid. We currently have a 100kW solar system underway at Val De Vie Estate in Stellenbosch.

